  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You constrict and bind a creature with metal, choose one creature in range, they must make a Strength saving throw, being Restrained by the metal prison and unable to cast jutsu with the HS component on a failed Save. The metal prison has an AC equal to your Ninjutsu Save DC and 200 Hit Points. The metal prison is resistant to all damage excluding lightning damage. A creature can attempt to remake the Strength Saving throw at the end of each of their turns to end being restrained. Each time a creature fails the strength saving throw the DC increases by 4 to a max of +20.</p>",
